article_title: New York Sen. Dean Skelos to Cooperate With Federal Inquiry
article_text:
New York state Senate leader Dean Skelos said Thursday he would cooperate with investigators in the wake of reports that they are probing him and his son as part of a wider look into corruption in Albany.
